          .sponsors
            h3.h2 Sponsor CEDDL Polyfill.

            p CEDDL Polyfill is an MIT licensed open source project and completely free to use. However, the amount of effort needed to write specs, maintain, develop features for the project is not sustainable without proper financial backing.

            p If you run a business and are using CEDDL Polyfill in a revenue-generating product, it makes business sense to sponsor development: it ensures the project that your product relies on stays healthy and end up being implemented in browsers. It can also help your exposure in the community and makes it easier to attract analytics and Data management platform developers and analysts.

